message: Let's start fair. I'm offering you 40% and I'll take 60%. What do you think?
Your offer was a bit unfair to me. Let's be more realistic. I propose I take 60% and you get 40%.
Okay, let's try to find a middle ground. I'm willing to take a little less.  I'll take 55% and you can have 45%.  Let's see if we can reach an agreement this time.
